data.name: ReadPersonProgramProgram1
data.value: select top(1) T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID, T2.CODE, T2.INTERSTATE_IND from CKT_PROGRAM T2 join CKT_PERSON_PROGRAM T1 on (T2.PROGRAM_ID = T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE > @discontinueDate) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE < @effectiveDate) and (T2.PROGRAM_ID = @programId)

data.name: ReadPersonProgramProgram2
data.value: select top(1) T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID, T2.CODE, T2.INTERSTATE_IND from CKT_PROGRAM T2 join CKT_PERSON_PROGRAM T1 on (T2.PROGRAM_ID = T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate1) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate1) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE < @effectiveDate2)

data.name: ReadPersonProgramProgram3
data.value: select T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID, T2.CODE, T2.INTERSTATE_IND from CKT_PROGRAM T2 join CKT_PERSON_PROGRAM T1 on (T2.PROGRAM_ID = T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate1) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate1) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE < @effectiveDate2) and ( T2.PROGRAM_ID in (cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier1 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier2 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier3 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier4 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier5 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier6 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier7 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier8 as smallint)) )

data.name: ReadPersonProgramProgram4
data.value: select T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID, T2.CODE, T2.INTERSTATE_IND from CKT_PROGRAM T2 join CKT_PERSON_PROGRAM T1 on (T2.PROGRAM_ID = T1.PRG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE > @effectiveDate1) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate2) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE < @effectiveDate3) and ( T2.PROGRAM_ID in (cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier1 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier2 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier3 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier4 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier5 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier6 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier7 as smallint), cast(@systemGeneratedIdentifier8 as smallint)) ) order by T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE
